  {
    "client_msg_id": "af08e331-33a7-4ae2-9c28-7638a9adeb8c",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hey Michael! I previously enjoyed reading some of your blogs like \"Against software development\". Given some of the themes you mentioned (interaction of small computing elements), you might be interested in this old paper: <http://maya.com/content/publications/0034-the-trillion-node-network/maya_trillion_node_network.pdf>\n\nTowards the end it proposes attribute/values as the next step above bytes as the basis of interoperability, and one might argue that in the intervening years that has been at least somewhat imperfectly realized by the widespread adoption of JSON APIs",
